headline: Why Serve Robotics is acquiring a hospital assistant robot company
summary: Serve Robotics is expanding beyond its sidewalk delivery roots by acquiring Diligent Robotics, which makes a hospital assistant bot named Moxi.

headline: Milan Kovac Joins DoorDash Board of Directors
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, January 20, 2026--DoorDash, Inc. (NASDAQ: DASH) announced today that Milan Kovac, former Vice President of Optimus Robotics and Autopilot at Tesla, has been appointed to the company’s Board of Directors, effective January 16, 2026.

headline: Serve Robotics: Multibillion-Dollar Ambition Comes With Uncertainty (Upgrade)
summary: Serve Robotics Inc. is scaling fast toward 2,000 robots and a 1M goal. Click for this updated look at SERV stock and see why it merits an upgrade.

headline: Grubhub parent acquires restaurant rewards app Claim
summary: The delivery platform will integrate Claim’s technology, which helps restaurants acquire high-value, long-term customers, within its platform later this year.
